What you need to know:

Among those who have condoled with the family are Sports Cabinet Secretary Amina Mohamed, Sports Principal Secretary Joe Okudo and ministry officials led by Chief of Staff Rose WachukaNation Media Group Chief Executive Officer Stephen Gitagama and Group Editorial Director Mutuma Mathiu have led the Group in condoling with Makori and his familyVarious federation officials, including federation presidents Waithaka Kioni (volleyball), Jackson Tuwei (athletics) and Nick Mwendwa (football) also sent their messages of sympathy